            "title": "半日收市︱先升後跌 恒指跌71點報26851點 保險股受壓 創科回歸「紅底股」",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股再次未能企穩兩萬七關口，早市高開低走倒跌收場。保險與多數重磅科股均偏軟，部份二線藍籌則突圍而出，創科實業(00669)便重越百元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：創科實業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113930_source-web_00669創科實業-logo_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：創科實業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113930_source-web_00669創科實業-logo_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：創科實業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早跟隨外圍高開，於競價時段已重越27000點，以27094點開市，開市未幾升幅擴大至252點，衝上見27176點卻無以為繼，隨即迅速回落並於上午約10時再新轉跌失守27000點，並進入約1小時的好淡爭持階段，於上午11時過後一直維持跌市，最低報26839點，倒跌83點。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：創科實業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113930_source-web_00669創科實業-logo_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：創科實業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113930_source-web_00669創科實業-logo_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：創科實業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：創科實業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113930_source-web_00669創科實業-logo_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：創科實業官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指中午收報26851點，跌71點或0.27%。恒生科技指數也跌12點或0.22%，報5815點；國企指數跌37點或0.4%，報9229點。主板半日成交1407.9億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌55點，報26878點，高水26點。科指期貨跌10點，報5824點，高水8點。國指期貨跌34點，報9237點，高水7點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅保險股是拖低大市的主力，友邦(01299)挫2%，報83.15元，單一股份已拖低恒指逾29點。兩隻藍籌內險股亦向下，中國平安(02318)跌1.58%，報68.45元；中國人壽(02628)再回吐1.2%，報31.38元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藍籌科股跌多於升，快手(01024)落實發行美元及人民幣優先票據規模，股價今早高開後迅速轉跌，中午收報77.8元，跌2.2%；百度(09888)也回吐0.41%，報145.6元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「ATMXJ」有4隻報跌，跌幅最大的是近期相對弱勢的小米(01810)，跌1.59%，報37.26元；京東(09618)跌0.96%，報114元；騰訊(00700)跌0.8%，報617元；美團(03690)中午收市前跌至半日低位100元收市，跌0.79%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)是「ATMXJ」當中今早唯一逆市回升的成員，半日低位165.3元時仍升0.43%，最高報168.7元，升2.49%；中午收報166.4元，升1.09%，令恒指跌少24點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司昨天早上宣布千問App重大升級，又披露上線兩個月內月度活躍用戶已破億，該股昨天雖然回吐，但卻獲不少券商唱好。摩根士丹利便認為，阿里千問具備成為超級App優勢，重申對該股「增持」評級。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一邊廂，連日與阿里巴巴保持相同升跌方向的阿里健康(00241)，今早非但未能再被「帶挈」回升，更成為藍籌表現包尾，半日跌5.44%，報6.78元；京東健康(06618)也跌2.14%，報66.45元。泡泡瑪特(09992)則在藍籌中排尾二，跌4.76%，報180.2元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日前爆出因為涉壟斷遭市場監管總局立案調查的攜程(09961)，經前兩日累計挫逾24%後，今早仍反覆偏軟，初段曾反彈最多1.74%、高見468元，早市中段開始倒跌，中午收報458.8元，跌0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">事實上，今早確有逾半恒指成分股報跌，而在逆市報升的藍籌當中，滙控(00005)是令對恒指提供第2大點數進賬的股份，升0.55%，報128.9元，令恒指跌少13點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">表現最佳藍籌落在創科實業身上，該股甫開市即回歸「紅底股」行列，開報101.1元，升2.64%，最高報103.6元，升5.18%；中午收報102.7元，仍漲4.26%。李寧(02331)獲高盛等券商上調目標價，該股今早亦漲3.73%，報20.28元，成表現次佳藍籌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15587068-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%85%88%e5%8d%87%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c71%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126851%e9%bb%9e-%e4%bf%9d%e9%9a%aa%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93-%e5%89%b5",
