            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">天任集團(01429)早市中途停牌，之前該股大幅抽升，停牌前報0.185元，飆68.18%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"天任集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01429-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"天任集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01429-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">天任集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股於上午10時09分起停牌；股份今早裂口高開14.55%，以0.126元開市即見今日低位，最高曾衝上0.24元，急升1.18倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，天鴿互動(01980)則於今早開市前已停牌。</p>\n</div>",
